headline: Why The Trade Desk Stock Popped 40% in May
summary: After missing fourth-quarter estimates, The Trade Desk redeemed itself with a strong first-quarter earnings report.  The stock also gained as the U.S. and China agreed to lower tariff rates.  The Trade Desk has made significant investments in AI, which should set it up for success over the long term.
